{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":7,"isBulletin":561},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5,"uri":6},"Sicile","Orsi","1896","\u003Cspan>Paolo Orsi, « Sicile », \u003Ci>Bulletin de Correspondance Hellénique\u003C/i> 20 (1896): 399‑400\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/FWX5CWBN",[8,116,170,256,322,387],{"file":9,"uri":9,"title":10,"status":11,"editionAuthor":13,"type":14,"objectType":18,"material":22,"condition":26,"layoutDesc":27,"handNote":34,"date":50,"places":55,"geo":65,"country":60,"provenance":57,"provenanceGeo":69,"region":72,"settlement":73,"repository":74,"idno":78,"textLang":81,"tmNumber":26,"letterHeights":85,"publications":89,"zotero":93,"keywords":97,"html":108,"bibl":109,"bulletinDateSort":115,"citedRangeSort":110,"languageSort":82,"materialSort":23,"typeSort":15},"ISic001869","Funerary inscription for Artemo",{"_":12},"edited",null,{"_":15,"ana":16,"ref":17},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":19,"ana":20,"ref":21},"block","#object.block","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/189.html",{"_":23,"ana":24,"ref":25},"limestone","#material.stone.limestone","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html","",{"layout":28},{"p":29,"rs":30,"damage":26},"Three lines of Greek letters, seemingly not centered / regularly laid out.",{"_":31,"ana":32,"ref":33},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":35,"dimensions":36},"Described by Orsi (1896) as 'scritto a pessimi caratteri', and (1899) as 'lettere cattive, rustiche cosi che a tutta prima sembrano archaiche, e molto sconservate... L'iscrizione negligentemente redatta e scolpita è funebre di tarda età'. Pace states 'lettere del III sec. av. Cr.', but given the presence of lunate epsilon and Orsi's comments, a later date seems much more likely.",[37,46],{"type":38,"l":39,"fro